  <brief_title>Evaluate the Efficacy of AMG 706 to Treat Advanced Gastrointestinal Stromal Tumors</brief_title>
  <official_title>An Open-label Phase 2 Study of AMG 706 in Japanese Subjects With Advanced Gastrointestinal Stromal Tumors (GISTs) Who Developed Progressive Disease or Relapsed While on Imatinib Mesylate</official_title>
