  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to evaluate the safety and efficacy of AMG 706 in patients with
      gastrointestinal stromal tumor that have not been controlled while taking imatinib mesylate.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
